title: Mr. Perfectly Fine (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
Mr. Perfectly Fine is such a bop and people think they know who she's singing about.. and why she said 'Mr." as many times as she did.. but some fans speculate this song could be about someone else! What are all of the theories? Listen as Nick, Amy, Ana and Lacey break this song down!
What did we miss? What album should we break down next? Let us know!
